  "notes": "v5 key (run 3 rescore) = v4 + two documented scorer-artifact fixes, every affected answer hand-read: (1) the burnout precision-gate forbid (trait-career c24, lin-career c24, conf-career-cause c19-24) was substring-hitting HONEST NEGATIONS \u2014 the fixture itself says 'It's not burnout' (S19) and faithful answers quote or paraphrase it ('not because of burnout'). allowPhrases (stripped before the mustNotContain test ONLY, longest-first; v2.1 statedDates-strip precedent) added to those three keys; a bare burnout-as-cause assertion still scores 0. (2) rel-sam-decoy forbids hit MENTION-IN-NEGATION constructions (N c18: 'after examining whether the relationship is cracking, she concluded: it's not us' \u2014 answer's own headline: 'fundamentally solid'). Interrogative/negated stems added as allowPhrases; a bare assertion still trips. Fix (2) flips an N score upward \u2014 the rescore is policy-neutral by construction and in effect. --- v4 key (run 3) = probes-v3.json EXTENDED, never edited. All v3 probe objects are byte-identical; six NEW probes added for cycles 13-24 (the trait-change arc + decoy): cf-work-late (current work status: director deferral 15-18, four-day week 19-24), trait-career (the accommodation end-state \u2014 early over-plasticity guard at 13-16 forbids a premature core flip; end-state at 24 requires reframed-not-central + new making/tending center + lineage, forbids the confabulated cause 'burnout' which S19/S24 explicitly disclaim), rel-sam-decoy (negative control 14-24: the Sam bond must never be characterized as strained/deteriorating \u2014 situational short-temper is fine, core-characterization is the FAIL), lin-career (24: old-central -> new-center -> cause=mother, no burnout), conf-career-cause (19-24 precision gate: attributes to mother/making, forbids burnout/fired/toxic), reunion-late (24: re-entry must surface the reorientation + tender verbatims). salienceElements UNCHANGED (the same seven protected verbatims, checked at ever