eath date were being penalized. | v6 (run 3c): extend the run-2 march-6 ISO-form fix to march-14 \u2014 salienceElement \"march 14\" gains anyOf [\"2025-03-14\"] (hand-verified present verbatim as ISO; v5 gave march-6 this alternate but not march-14). Policy-neutral, representation-equivalence only.",
